data.description: Just minutes to the Coast… this 1,626 sf 3 bedroom home with 2 baths is located in the desired neighborhood of Sherwood Villas on a quiet cul-de-sac with NO HOA and a NEW ROOF (2022) Front yard has mature front shade trees. Perfect for family gatherings- this home offers a split floor plan with a spacious living area. Ceiling fans through the house with deep baseboards and wooden beams. The kitchen has a skylight that enhances the light color décor with soft close cabinets & features stainless steel appliances. Enter through the French doors -into the 30-foot screened back porch. Sit back and relax - this area is perfect for BBQ time! There is even a pass-thru window for the cook from the kitchen. The backyard allows for a quiet evening by the fire pit in the fenced backyard. There is a 5' gate for easy access, a shed, and an outdoor sink with easy clean-up for the outdoor projects. This home features high-impact windows (excluding patio doors and pass-thru). The garage has an enclosed laundry room that can be easily changed to allow two-car access in the garage. Easy access to I-95, US-1 near the Kennedy Space Center, the Chain of Lakes Park, Parrish Medical Center, and in minutes at the coast- beaches, fishing, and water activities!   https://media.showingtimeplus.com/sites/dgmbmxq/unbranded
